{"tid":672880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尷尬！貝拿迪亞跟美女握手被拒","createTime":"2018-05-21T11:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T12:42:33.000Z","uid":1121,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e587a2e93dff90b8619d3cf03434a796f60428f0","tid":672880,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/191154_1eb7df75663711c7670bcb1f6e9788c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F191154_1eb7df75663711c7670bcb1f6e9788c9.png&h=dfcfe1e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=udWQ8CAbBnyBdUhumdbJwNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b1b5f63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】意甲冠軍在手就一定獲美女青睞？未必！<br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯早就確定意甲7連霸，在周六煞科戰主場以2:1擊敗維羅納後，舉行了捧盃儀式，一眾球員一個跟一個走上頒獎台，接受加冕，威風八面。<br />\n<br />\n可是，中堅貝拿迪亞（Mehdi Benatia）走上台時，伸出右手欲跟頒獎台旁邊2名扮演「禮儀小姐」角色的美女模特兒握手時，卻慘「食檸檬」，金髮美女更搖搖頭，而黑髮的另一人就只是保持笑容，尷尬得這名摩洛哥國腳立即縮手。2名美女拒絕握手，很大機會是因為賽會規定他們不能夠跟球員有身體接觸，而不是31歲的貝拿迪亞魅力不足。<br />\n<br />\n美女不識貨不要緊，有傳貝拿迪亞大把球會吼，但他表示：「我還有2年合約，會先專注踢好世界，之後再作出對自己及祖記最好的選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"006c50195b11ea52240f619bf9d441787a512bc0","tid":672880,"uid":1121,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/9735cb93f68932465ed04970d498266c/tenor.gif?itemid=10741539\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F9735cb93f68932465ed04970d498266c%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D10741539&h=d6602cd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7042c6f7f2ea699ae28a750a34156bacda00af63","tid":672880,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe06c47dfc9f2bbba7c801ff67359633dd118863","tid":672880,"uid":1121,"lik